subject: Football
College Athletics
organizations: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: David Wilson returned a kickoff 90 yards for a touchdown with 2 minutes 23 seconds to play, and No. 20 Virginia Tech held on to beat Georgia Tech, 28-21, in Blacksburg, Va.
